cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DL 

The paper deals with neural network compression for computer vision tasks, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of reinforcement learning and policy gradients also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with deep neural networks (cs.NE) and their architecture (cs.DL), which further supports these sub-categories.
